data.description: This 4 bedroom 2 bath completely remodeled home showcases a very modern open concept.  The dining, family and living room are all together in one space with a 4th bedroom on the other side of the house behind the garage.  All new plumbing drains, brand new roof, laminate flooring, doors & trim, updated baths and countertops make this home feel like it was just built.  You'll enjoy the large trussed screen porch, oversized bedrooms and wide fenced in lot with mature landscaping giving this home lending its own individual design.
